{"article_id":"dOlZ2hFokTtP6MRE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Trump set off another spat with the United Kingdom on Friday with tweets","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that appeared to blame British security for a terrorist attack .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"They drew a swift rebuke from Prime Minister Theresa May .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"`` I never think","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"it 's helpful for anybody to speculate on what is an ongoing investigation , ''","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"May told reporters in London .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"During an early-morning tweet barrage , Trump said","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"security officials need to be more aggressive in thwarting terrorists .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"`` Another attack in London by a loser terrorist .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"These are sick and demented people","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"who were in the sights of Scotland Yard .","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"Must be proactive ! ''","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"Trump tweeted ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"implying","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that British authorities also knew the identity","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"of who planted a bomb on a London subway .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"White House Spokeswoman Sarah Sanders said","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Trump and May later spoke by phone .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Police in London said","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"an explosive","depth":14},{"id":21,"text":"planted by a terrorist","depth":14},{"id":22,"text":"blew up on a train","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"as it pulled into a London subway station during rush hour .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"The blast injured 22 people ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"but there were no deaths .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"Police engaged in manhunt for what they described as an isolated incident .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"So far , however , no suspects have been identified","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"or whether anyone was involved was being tracked by Scotland Yard ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"which is similar to the FBI .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"`` Loser terrorists must be dealt with in a much tougher manner .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The internet is their main recruitment tool","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"which we must cut off","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"& use better ! ''","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"As the tweets gained steam ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"London police also weighed in ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"saying in a statement","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that `` any speculation is unhelpful . ''","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Speaking later with reporters in the Rose Garden ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Trump called the attack `` a terrible thing . '","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"' `` it keeps going and going ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and we have to be very smart","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"and we have to be very , very tough -","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"perhaps we ' re not nearly tough enough ,","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"he said . `` We have to be smarter . ''","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"This is n't the first time","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Trump has triggered a dispute with a British government official over security .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"After a June attack in London , Trump misconstrued a statement by London Mayor Sadiq Khan ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"and mocked him","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"for claiming","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"there was `` no reason","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"to be alarmed . ''","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Khan said","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"he was referring to enhanced police protection in the area","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"following that attack .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"At that time , May said","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"that the mayor `` is doing a good job","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"and it ' s wrong to say anything else .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"He ' s doing a good job . ''","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"In his tweet storm on Friday , Trump also called for a tougher travel ban to the United States .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"A tweet about the proposed ban on travel to the United States from residents of six mostly Muslim countries","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"- Iran , Libya , Somalia , Sudan , Syria and Yemen -","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"called for even tougher measures ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"but said","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"they would not be `` politically correct . ''","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"The ban ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"initially announced on Jan. 27 ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"has been reworked","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"and fought in a variety of federal courts .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"it will be heard by the U.S. Supreme Court","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"when it starts its new term next month .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"The court will hear arguments next month in the broader constitutional challenge to the travel ban from states and immigrant rights groups .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"The current dispute is over which immigrants and refugees can enter in the meantime .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Trump did not specify the tougher measures","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"he had in mind .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Also ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"since authorities in London have not identified","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"who is behind Friday 's bombing ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"it is not known whether that attack had anything to do with residents of the six countries","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"covered by the ban .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"British officials :","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"'Incident ' on London Underground train was terror attack","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":85,"text":"Trump 's 'TRAVEL 